Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:24.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}待てよ！　邪悪な牙を剥いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:30.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}嗤う　悪のデスアーマー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:36.64,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺が！　俺たちが許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:42.50,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危険上等　ブレイブチェンジ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:48.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剣戦隊ブレードブレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:24.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs22}住手吧！  剝下邪惡的爪牙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:30.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs22}嗤笑著  邪惡的Death Armour
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:36.64,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我不能！  我們不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:42.50,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}危險最高  Brave Change!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:48.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}超劍戰隊 Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超劍戰隊  Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮正在被襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的Death Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不可能贏的了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕！Death Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要打倒你  讓世界恢復和平！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第2話\NBlade Braver和便當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？新部員？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一年級的川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劍道經驗的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來測試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  把你捲入到奇怪的事情裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山啊  只要一有人入部首先就會去打倒對方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此來明示上下級關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對女生也是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  如果是女生他更會去欺負
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山是個虐待狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女在一起活動的運動部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次男生都囂張得無法無天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那些傢伙都把社團活動\N當成正大光明顯示自己力量絕佳的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  小珠！去打倒他  我們社團那個最大的壞人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去給那個一直欺負我們的外山一點顏色看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…紀梨乃學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道服…沒有其他的了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件已經是最小的了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…我太矮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面雖然可以折起來…但後面拖著會踩到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還是算了吧…回頭等你把自己的拿來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一定要比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只有今天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別回去啊  一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我教訓了她就輪到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是小學時候的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被高年級的學生給圍住  打了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的一個人拿起鐵管亂揮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候  她出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個正義的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  就是小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義的伙伴啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊  那麼…開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山的竹刀可是碳素的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給打到可是很疼的哦  要是被擊中前臂什麼的簡直就是下地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這傢伙因為喜歡看對方痛苦的表情所以才使用碳素棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  真差勁  真是惡劣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…川添同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意岩佐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放輕鬆點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也不是正式比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太認真對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道這只是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義的伙伴…英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西也不能當飯吃啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到了遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！面！面！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度還挺快的  我都打不中啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真來打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道本身在得取一本的時候  要回到原地重整姿態才是應有禮儀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不重整姿態嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不說了麼  又不是比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看看你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  又不是拿到一本就算獲勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山只是想打人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個虐待狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道的目的不是砍人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是通過學習劍術的道理  參悟武士的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非以打倒對方為目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了提升自己進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.40,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小珠  4歲）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  對你來說太早了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  希望你能瞭解  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道是以禮開始以禮結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最重視禮儀的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那時候起已經11年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也到了我不瞭解她的年齡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼晚了 她在學校發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  攻過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一般的劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣！根本不痛不癢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太弱小了！這種攻擊根本無效！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀…果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙褲太長  所以後面會踩住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  所以動作不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用力踩住  好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣正好  外山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不方便後退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就緊逼著上前打倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她好好明白比力氣是贏不過男人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連汗都沒有流…真不爽！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果靠我的力量  無論擊中幾次都是無效
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的刺擊力道太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像要給壞人最後一擊一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能使用刺擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰都不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年長的男人應該可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然僅限於學過劍道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且要等你上高中後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前就封印起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學過劍道的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成為…高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦  回去吃碗拉麵慢慢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這種事情也很容易突然莫名其妙的就搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  外山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是輸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑倒了嗎  你還真誇張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個不知道什麼時候還會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候能與之抗衡的…就只有你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道能盡多少力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義的伙伴  一年九班川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:13:02.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剣戦隊ブレードブレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:13:02.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}超劍戰隊 Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子火焰劍！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為這樣就結束了  Blade Braver！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管幾次我都會復活的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼不管幾次我都保護給你看！人們的笑容！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬  那個是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加入劍道部了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能提起幹勁是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被朋友邀請去的嗎？還是說聽了老師建議？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了在壞人手中維護正義！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛發的複印件  下次交上來就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你沒什麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早飯也沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不趕快搞定和前輩的比賽  小命都要不保了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要吃麵包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是中午剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我正在減肥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！給我嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！好棒！麵包麵包！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下麵包星人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下麵包星人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是為了嚴格訓練準備的大分量便當
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是只為段郎特製的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有男子氣概呢  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家一起換著吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我的梅乾不能換著吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只有一個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過米飯的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我就吃點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家是開雜貨店的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  吃漢堡包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  小都都做的炸蝦條也很美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我右手的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  感覺像是在被喂飼料…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠還很小  得多吃點長得大點才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個二年級的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  她叫小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我國小國中高中一直一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她時常會這種的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟下一句「好好等待吧  時間會解決一切」就不見人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年我們劍道部是怎麼樣的情況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績這方面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很普通  團體戰能進二回戰就不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個人的話偶爾男生會進半決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生一直都一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有指導者的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙很懶惰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  最近開始有幹勁了我很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:30.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次國中時候怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好成績是縣八強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  一點都不厲害  沒什麼大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連縣大會都出場不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次都沒什麼大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這類的就是廢物了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很厲害的  我很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大會這類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有出場過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  真浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不出場也知道結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國大賽優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上桑原鞘子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要一個能成戰力的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  首先得製作特訓的計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有幹勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  吉川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你最近一直都沒什麼幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很讓人擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近學生和老師都沒有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  有點像笨蛋那樣熱血比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點熱情過剩  只要能將學生指引到正確方向就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  就無法說出動機了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你說了打擊要只靠手腕用力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～對不起  都成習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個示範給她看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這才像真正的劍道部～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滴淌的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛舞的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀟灑的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你那是什麼品味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有示範了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀放輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  再示範一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  段和小都都有在跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  在外面跑圈中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎  要落後了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個傢伙首先得從基礎體力開始鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…在附近的話感覺會很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小都都可是要在練習比賽中出場的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點進行針對比賽的練習可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的實力還沒有在實戰中確認過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  認真的放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  不可以的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師怎麼說也算是有自尊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能秒殺他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就算要贏也多少讓他揮兩下再贏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連我也…生疏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師有幹勁了  我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬  又收到了媽媽老家的特產
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  從我老家寄來了梅子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你最喜歡的  紀州有機梅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要做成三明治分給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃光芒萬丈不可違抗的Death Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你們正面傳授三條死亡界的信條吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:23:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一  不要有所好惡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.97,0:24:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二  時刻要有反抗的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.99,0:24:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三  即使是跟你很親切的人也不要去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　　　　 offence　　　 defence{\r}\N其四  要進攻首先要防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.89,0:24:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有四條  但是不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能夠遵守好這四條的話\N你也能成為了不起的Death Boy了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.09,0:24:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身穿Death Metal用Deathice發揮Death的效果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的標題是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「BLACK和BLUE」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.88,0:24:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我沒有上場  不看也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.98,0:24:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚～
